=====================================================================================
Section 1 : Information regarding the TBB-VECT-VECT-MALLOC directory structure.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
include/       --> consists of header files
src/           --> contains README file and main file
                   README - Gives quick information regarding Package and how to execute
                   the code.
lib/           --> contains file having function definitions.

===================================================================================
Section 2 : Steps for using  TBB-VECT-VECT-MALLOC
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Copy the "TBB-VECT-VECT-MALLOC.tar". Untar the file using
         $tar -xvf  TBB-VECT-VECT-MALLOC


in your home directory. This will create folder "TBB-VECT-VECT-MALLOC"

The following directory structure of  TBB-VECT-VECT-MALLOC  will be created in the
main directory i.e "TBB-VECT-VECT-MALLOC".

          /include        /src          /lib


===================================================================================
Section 3 : Pre-Requisites.
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

TBB2.0 should be installed and configured with Linux /Unix OS.

=====================================================================================
Section 4 : Steps for compiling  TBB-VECT-VECT-MALLOC
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Go in the respective directory
and give
         make

==================================================================================
Section 5 : Steps for executing  TBB-VECT-VECT-MALLOC
----------------------------------------------------------------------------------

	./name_of_executable  size  Number-of-threads


